title: NFL Draft: Top 5 Tight End and Offensive Line Prospects with Pete Prisco (Football 4/10)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Pete Prisco as 'offensive prospect rankings week' on the Pick Six podcast concludes. Pete ranks his Top 5 tight ends and Top 5 offensive lineman in the 2020 Draft. When will the first TE go off the board? How many OL will be selected in the first round? How about the Top 10? Next week, we'll be dissecting the top defensive prospects in this year's class.
'Pick Six' is available on Apple Podcasts, Spotify, Stitcher, Google Podcasts, Castbox and wherever else you listen to podcasts.
